Frets-on-Fire C++ is a rewrite in C++ of the Frets-on-Fire game.

Songs are not included, but scripts and tools for automatically
downloading these songs are provided under windows (dlsongs directory).

The game is work-in-progress, some things are known not to work
at this time.

Things that work:
 * playing
 * score computation more or less compatible with FoF
 * whammy
 * game controller (guitar)
 * split screen multiplayer
 * basic settings
 * fullscreen
 * stage animations and lights
 
Things that do not work:
 * network play
